snippet.title: Forest's Secret Trailer
snippet.description:
Forest's Secret is a free, cozy, nonviolent adventure game developed by me and coming out in on December 30th, 2018! Learn more about it here: https://bynine.itch.io/forestssecret  

Trailer created by the wonderful https://twitter.com/jarrod__roberts  with the backing guitar track provided by my friend John!
